==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Putting green
<hw>Putt"ing green</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Golf)</fld> <def>The green,
or plot of smooth turf, surrounding a hole.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The term
<xex>putting green</xex> shall mean the ground within twenty yards of
the hole, excepting hazards.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Golf Rules.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Puttock</ent>⟦br⟧
